WHy Recursion?
ANs : It helps us in Solving bigger/ Complex problems in a simple way .

You can convert Recursion solutions into iterations and vice versa .

Space Complexity : is not constant beacuse of calls

it helps us in breakig down bigger problems to smaller problems


 Question :Find nth Fibonacci number


Brak it down to smaller problem and make a reccurance relation
the base condition is represented with the answer we already have


